#: ../../source/unit/nbiot.rst:332 76bf05e139b7457a8380b0b6bf552cef
msgid "Send an HTTP request."
msgstr "发送 HTTP 请求。"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot.rst:334 b40f03b2e6a048c4bfe3ca487a5397a5
msgid "HTTP method to use (e.g. \"GET\", \"POST\")."
msgstr "要使用的 HTTP 方法（例如 \"GET\"、\"POST\"）。"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot.rst:335 9fbe718eb43c409bbe42256b36943482
msgid "URL to send the request to."
msgstr "用于发送请求的 URL。"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot.rst:336 9b3a21056d1a4145ba1f7a652cff59c1
msgid ""
"(optional) Dictionary, list of tuples, bytes, or file-like object to send"
" in the body of the Request."
msgstr "（可选）用于在 Request 请求体中发送的字典、元组列表、bytes 或类文件对象。"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot.rst:337 2127847aee46444999ba6bc396d112ce
msgid ""
"(optional) A JSON serializable Python object to send in the body of the "
"Request."
msgstr "（可选）要在 Request 的正文中发送的可 JSON 序列化的 Python 对象。"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot.rst:338 e1549b0553ea4561a31b8d24fc5e7e17
msgid "(optional) Dictionary of HTTP Headers to send with the Request."
msgstr "（可选）要随请求一起发送的 HTTP Headers 字典。"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot.rst:339 b113ebba7790417e83e87357b2d07e7d
msgid "(optional) if False, the response content will be immediately downloaded."
msgstr "（可选）如果为 False，响应内容将立即下载。"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot.rst:340 af1ff81800744e82ba9edaccf3c95928
msgid "(optional) Auth tuple to enable Basic/Digest/Custom HTTP Auth."
msgstr "（可选）用于启用 Basic/Digest/Custom HTTP Auth 的 Auth 元组。"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot.rst:341 fb9f6c2470694c7484d7fcb8e38768bd
msgid ""
"(optional) How many seconds to wait for the server to send data before "
"giving up."
msgstr "（可选）在放弃之前等待服务器发送数据的秒数。"

#: ../../source/unit/nbiot.rst:342 6da4ff92406740d3b9cfe3ba4f4fda16
msgid "(optional) Whether to parse response headers."
msgstr "（可选）是否解析响应头。"

